"One Hell of a Gamble", Timothy Naftali and Aleksandr Fursenko, 1997
documents Bill Walton's visit to Moscow just after the assasination
and the message he carried from Bobby Kennedy to Georgi Bolshakov,
including his views on the assasination and his plans for his political
future.

"Brothers", David Talbot, Free Press, 2007
documents Bobby Kennedy's story through 1961 to his death, including
his judgements on who killed his brother.
